content: wtfsayo: Delivered a high volume of work this week, primarily focused on enhancing the client-side agent experience while also addressing various bugs and chores across the system. Their most significant contributions were two major features in the `elizaos/eliza` repository: adding an agent runs visualization timeline (#6016) and a substantial enhancement to the agent runs sidebar (#6023, +17k lines). Alongside this feature development, they merged several fixes and chores, including disabling a local endpoint in production (#6014) and adding a new plugin to the registry (#234), demonstrating a broad focus on both new functionality and system maintenance.
